name: Dogenerates
description: A new symbol of unity, freedom, and community — inspired by Elon Musk’s vision as the founder of the America Party. We stand for open innovation, transparency, and the power of everyday people to shape the future together. Backed by the spirit of Doge and the belief that laughter and progress can go hand in hand, Dogenerates is more than a meme — it’s a movement for real change. Join us. Be part of the story Elon started.
